{
  "stem": "23410.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But also Denmark, because they knew when the action will be.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Hungary.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Jews were in Poland, let's run away to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But in Poland, they said, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We are not going to collaborate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they were taken and being shot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we undug their grave to burn them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we only knew that they were Polish because we found the inscriptions and so on on their pens and paper.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Professor Bartel, Ostrowski, Boy-Zelenski, a whole Polish leadership that was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this is why in Poland, it was so important that I am a witness again and again.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in Poland, they invited me, and so on, many times.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was Boy-Zelenski, Bartel, and so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was Yom Kippur evening, before Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yom Kippur evening in 1943.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- And for us, a lot of us, it was a question of self-respect, like, to keep something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "To be-- to-- to be a human being.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It wasn't for any religious, and so on, purposes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was more for us to be a human being.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I have something, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'm not giving in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we were treated very well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I don't mean that we weren't beaten here and there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we were treated-- we had enough food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not only enough, more than enough food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had leftover food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Plus, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] if they brought a group of 1,000 Jews, they told them exactly same as they brought it in '41, '42.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You are going to work someplace.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they took with them what they have left in food or in gold to bring with them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They came to us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And all this food or clothing was given to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What do you mean, why?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they needed a group to undig.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
